# Testing

## Workflow (TDD)
1. **Write failing tests first** ‚Äî tests define the contract before implementation begins.
2. Implement the minimum code needed to make tests pass.
3. Refactor, keeping all tests green.
4. **No feature is complete without passing tests.** Do not move to the next task until tests pass.

---

