### Test Commands

```bash
# Unit tests only (fast, no real listeners or GUI)
pytest tests/unit -v

# Integration tests
pytest tests/integration -v

# All tests with coverage
pytest tests/ --cov=. --cov-omit="tests/*" --cov-report=term-missing
```

