## Coverage Requirements

| Module | Minimum line coverage | Key scenarios to cover |
|---|---|---|
| `tracker.py` | ‚â• 95% | record() increments count; rolling window drops events older than 60 s; get_apm() returns correct value; thread-safety under concurrent record() calls |
| `tray.py` | ‚â• 80% | Icon image is generated without error; label reflects current APM; tray menu items trigger correct callbacks |
| `overlay.py` | ‚â• 80% | Label updates when APM changes; window stays always-on-top; display mode switch tears down and recreates correctly |
| `main.py` | ‚â• 70% | Correct display mode selected at startup; graceful shutdown on exit signal |

